      • test

        public void test()
        This performs the actual create and update test given a count and update probability. Each create is accompanied by only a single update session on the object.
        Parameters:
        count - The number of create operations to perform; there will be one update per create
        updateProb - The probability for a particular field in the generated AbstractDataType to be randomly changed
